Sentencas: Sm-doped CeO2-Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9(SDC) electrolyte powders were prepared by using glycine-nitrate process, solid-state process and citric-nitrate process, respectively.
Titulo: Research on the Performance of Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9(SDC) Prepared by Different Methods

Sentencas: These three kinds of SDC powders were deposited onto the NiO-SDC anode substrates by colloidal spray coating technique.
Titulo: Research on the Performance of Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9(SDC) Prepared by Different Methods

Sentencas: The single cell was completed after screen printing the BSCF cathode on the SDC electrolyte film.
Titulo: Research on the Performance of Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9(SDC) Prepared by Different Methods

Sentencas: The performance of the single cell was tested by the CHI604B electrochemical work station.
Titulo: Research on the Performance of Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9(SDC) Prepared by Different Methods

Sentencas: The granularity distribution of the SDC powders was analyzed by the HORIBA LA-920 and the microstructure of the cell was investigated by SEM.
Titulo: Research on the Performance of Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9(SDC) Prepared by Different Methods

Sentencas: Results show that SDC electrolyte powders made by citric-nitrate process is content with the colloidal spray coating technique for SOFCS.
Titulo: Research on the Performance of Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9(SDC) Prepared by Different Methods
